                     project‚Üźbuff
                 :EndIf
                 ind‚Üź(‚éēC list[;1])‚ć≥‚äā‚éēC project
             :EndIf
             :If ind>‚ČĘlist
                 ind‚Üźlist[;2]‚ć≥‚äāF.NormalizePath project
             :EndIf
